<sect1 id="md_docs_doxygen_doxygen_awesome_css_README_1autotoc_md39">
<title>Browser support</title>
<para>Tested with</para>
<para><itemizedlist>
<listitem><para>Chrome 119, Chrome 119 for Android, Chrome 119 for iOS</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Safari 17, Safari for iOS 16</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Firefox 118, Firefox 120 for Android, Firefox 119 for iOS</para>
</listitem><listitem><para>Edge 119</para>
</listitem></itemizedlist>
</para>
<para>The theme does not strive to be backward compatible with (significantly) older browser versions.</para>
</sect1>
